PN,39201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777317067
OL,3,CCoroner rules woman's death as suicide
OL,4,Ccontributed to by gambling addiction
OL,6,FA coroner has concluded that a woman's
OL,7,Fgambling addiction contributed to her
OL,8,Fsuicide.
OL,10,FEllen Mulvey, who lived in Cheshire,
OL,11,Fsometimes spent all her wages on
OL,12,Fgambling after falling into financial
OL,13,Fdifficulties following a breakup of a
OL,14,Frelationship.
OL,16,FHM Area Coroner Elizabeth Wheeler
OL,17,Ffound that Ellen met the criteria for
OL,18,Fgambling disorder and that gambling
OL,19,Fwas a factor which contributed to her
OL,20,Fdeath.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777317067
OL,3,CCoroner rules woman's death as suicide
OL,4,Ccontributed to by gambling addiction
OL,6,FEllen's bank statements showed that
OL,7,Fher gambling-related transactions
OL,8,Facross licensed and unlicensed
OL,9,Foperators ran into the tens of
OL,10,Fthousands of pounds between 2018 and
OL,11,F2025.
OL,13,FThe inquest heard that Ellen had tried
OL,14,Fto self-exclude via online platform
OL,15,FGAMSTOP, which blocks access to
OL,16,Fgambling with online operators
OL,17,Flicensed in Great Britain. Ellen was
OL,18,Fstill able to gamble with unlicensed
OL,19,Fplatforms, and did so until shortly
OL,20,Fbefore her death.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777317067
OL,3,CCoroner rules woman's death as suicide
OL,4,Ccontributed to by gambling addiction
OL,6,FShe died aged 44 in November 2025 at
OL,7,FMacclesfield District General Hospital.
OL,9,FEvidence from Ellen's partner Deanne
OL,10,FTomkins and her sister Katie Styring
OL,11,Fdescribed how the true extent of her
OL,12,Fgambling addiction was largely hidden
OL,13,Ffrom those closest to her, often
OL,14,Fmasked by other explanations for her
OL,15,Fdistress and financial difficulties.
OL,17,FDeanne Tomkins said: "Ellen had the
OL,18,Fbiggest heart. She was kind, deeply
OL,19,Fempathetic, and always put others
OL,20,Fbefore herself.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777317067
OL,3,CCoroner rules woman's death as suicide
OL,4,Ccontributed to by gambling addiction
OL,6,F"I truly believe she would still be
OL,7,Fhere today if it wasn't for the harm
OL,8,Fcaused by gambling. She was a loving
OL,9,Fpartner and incredible stepmum to my 4-
OL,10,Fyear-old son. So patient, so playful
OL,11,Fand just full of love.
OL,13,F"The memory she created will stay with
OL,14,Fus forever, but the reality is she
OL,15,Fshould still be here. She's been taken
OL,16,Faway from a young family who needed
OL,17,Fher and who now have to grow up
OL,18,Fwithout her."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777317067
OL,3,CCoroner rules woman's death as suicide
OL,4,Ccontributed to by gambling addiction
OL,6,FShe added: "We feel so much more can
OL,7,Fbe done to reduce the harm caused by
OL,8,Fgambling in the UK, we feel there
OL,9,Fneeds to be a proper public health
OL,10,Fapproach that better informs and
OL,11,Fprotects everyone.
OL,13,F"We also want to see those
OL,14,Fexperiencing harm being better
OL,15,Fsupported in a way that reduces stigma
OL,16,Fand shame.
OL,18,F"We're also deeply concerned about the
OL,19,Funregulated online gambling sites
OL,20,Ftargeting those who have taken steps
OL,21,Fto self-exclude like Ellen did.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777317067
OL,3,CCoroner rules woman's death as suicide
OL,4,Ccontributed to by gambling addiction
OL,6,F"That should not be possible, and this
OL,7,Fis an issue that needs to be a
OL,8,Fpriority for those in positions to act.
OL,10,F"How many more lives have to be lost
OL,11,Fbefore something changes?"
OL,13,FKatie Styring, Ellen's sister said:
OL,14,F"Ellen was the kindest, most
OL,15,Fcompassionate person that we know. She
OL,16,Fgave everything to the people she
OL,17,Floved and she was always the one
OL,18,Flifting others up.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777317067
OL,3,CCoroner rules woman's death as suicide
OL,4,Ccontributed to by gambling addiction
OL,6,F"No matter what she was facing
OL,7,Fherself, she was our protector. She
OL,8,Fwas our biggest supporter and the
OL,9,Fheart of our family.
OL,11,F'We would like Ellen's story to shine
OL,12,Fa light on how dangerous and
OL,13,Fdevastating gambling can be - to help
OL,14,Fbreak down the shame and the stigma,
OL,15,Fand prevent others losing their lives."
OL,17,FIn a statement, the Gambling
OL,18,FCommission said: "The Coroner did not
OL,19,Frequest information from us for the
OL,20,FInquest, so we do not hold detailed
OL,21,Finformation about this case.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777317067
OL,3,CCoroner rules woman's death as suicide
OL,4,Ccontributed to by gambling addiction
OL,6,F"We are deeply saddened to hear of the
OL,7,Fdeath of Ellen Mulvey, and our
OL,8,Fthoughts are with her family and
OL,9,Ffriends at this difficult time.
OL,11,F"We have a robust regulatory framework
OL,12,Fin place which requires licensed
OL,13,Foperators to identify signs of
OL,14,Fgambling-related harm and to take
OL,15,Fappropriate action to protect
OL,16,Fconsumers.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777317067
OL,3,CCoroner rules woman's death as suicide
OL,4,Ccontributed to by gambling addiction
OL,6,F"Addressing criminal activity and
OL,7,Funlicensed gambling market requires a
OL,8,Fcoordinated approach between the
OL,9,FCommission, domestic and international
OL,10,Fregulators, GamStop, licensed
OL,11,Foperators, technology platforms, the
OL,12,Ffinancial sector, and law enforcement
OL,13,Fbodies. We continue to strengthen this
OL,14,Fcollaboration to better protect
OL,15,Fconsumers.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777317067
OL,3,CCoroner rules woman's death as suicide
OL,4,Ccontributed to by gambling addiction
OL,6,F"We also welcome the Government's
OL,7,Frecent Budget commitment to support
OL,8,Fefforts to tackle illegal gambling.
OL,9,FThe investment of #26 million over the
OL,10,Fnext three years will enable the
OL,11,FCommission to build on and enhance its
OL,12,Fwork to disrupt illegal operators and
OL,13,Fprotect consumers."
OL,15,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,16,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,17,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,18,Four region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
